 for something more challenging: that's where anything can happen! You'll never run out of new lands to explore. Something will always be different.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646120/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.poster.avif?t=1726266252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646120/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.webm?t=1726266252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646120/extras/1c1d7e04e0d69d0824a9934a078e3b85.mp4?t=1726266252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
